    "body" : "<p>you could <code>JSONObject#has</code>, providing the <code>key</code> as input and check if the method returns <code>true</code> or <code>false</code>. You could also</p>\n\n<p>use <code>optString</code> instead of <code>getString</code>:</p>\n\n<blockquote>\n  <p>Returns the value mapped by name if it exists, coercing it if\n  necessary. Returns the empty string if no such mapping exists</p>\n</blockquote>\n"
