    "body" : "<p>just before read key check it like before read</p>\n\n<pre><code>JSONObject json_obj=new JSONObject(yourjsonstr);\nif(!json_obj.isNull(\"club\"))\n{\n  //it's contain value to be read operation\n}\nelse\n{\n  //it's not contain key club or isnull so do this operation here\n}\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>isNull function definition </p>\n\n<pre><code>Returns true if this object has no mapping for name or\nif it has a mapping whose value is NULL. \n</code></pre>\n\n<p>official documentation below link for <code>isNull</code> function</p>\n\n<p><a href=\"http://developer.android.com/reference/org/json/JSONObject.html#isNull(java.lang.String)\" rel=\"noreferrer\">http://developer.android.com/reference/org/json/JSONObject.html#isNull(java.lang.String)</a></p>\n"
