    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can try this to check wether the key exists or not:</p>\n\n<pre><code>JSONObject object = new JSONObject(jsonfile);\nif (object.containskey(\"key\")) {\n  object.get(\"key\");\n  //etc. etc.\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
